{"tid":198930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我沖涼會好似觸緊電","createTime":"2017-04-12T22:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T01:38:18.000Z","uid":13172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5e2e9b114926c2b7d02c8e500428ec3d485653","tid":198930,"uid":13172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:26:36.000Z","msg":"有觸電嘅感覺係大概半年前開始。<br />\n<br />\n每次沖涼因為用儲水式熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要慢慢推左加熱唔係沖既水越黎越凍。<br />\n<br />\n由半年前到，一摸個水龍頭都會有觸電既感覺，連好快手推一下都會有少少觸電。搞到好唔想掂個水龍頭但又唔得。<br />\n<br />\n到頭先屙完尿洗手，連洗手盤個水龍頭都觸電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 橫掂都開左個水咁當然洗埋手啦。點知我放左手濕水先，左手竟然觸電觸到我痛同痺，但我右手掂水又唔會觸電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我係咪以後左手都唔可以洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果個水龍頭電得越嚟越勁，我會唔會最後成為因洗手而電死既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想咁樣死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc697e4ebdb9be3067250ccd9bed27ec19a4c9d","tid":198930,"uid":22727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:38:24.000Z","msg":"咁係你屋企個水籠頭有事定你有事？<br />\n係出面有無觸電Feel？<br />\n或者有無其他人係你屋企有觸電Feel？"},{"pid":"27c4472b04078bf82521307a4d48aa47970f2af5","tid":198930,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:39:57.000Z","msg":"之前有單沖涼電死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c60770dc0624cc468cb17ea641710651a10ce","tid":198930,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:42:03.000Z","msg":"Check下水氣掣係咪function啦屌，同埋熱水爐"},{"pid":"7465c326cd376cf57b295c0eb970722256415182","tid":198930,"uid":13172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係你屋企個水籠頭有事定你有事？<br />\n係出面有無觸電Feel？<br />\n或者有無其他人係你屋企有觸電Feel？</blockquote><br />\n會令到我有麻痺嘅感覺。<br />\n屋企人今日先feel到。<br />\n出面完全冇咁樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b62594daec958b76a0a36b1e50c6096fb80a07a","tid":198930,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁係你屋企個水籠頭有事定你有事？<br />\n係出面有無觸電Feel？<br />\n或者有無其他人係你屋企有觸電Feel？</blockquote><br />\n會令到我有麻痺嘅感覺。<br />\n屋企人今日先feel到。<br />\n出面完全冇咁樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵隻它錶check下穩陣d喎"},{"pid":"5404cbbecd721b5ae3d27bbfa72fe0b19ddcf7b2","tid":198930,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:10:45.000Z","msg":"咁就快d搵人check啦<br />\n嚟緊仲要假期<br />\n仲問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03dac3196280cbb5180d6f976cbeda29f3009e","tid":198930,"uid":51585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:10:48.000Z","msg":"一樣係電熱水龍 <br />\n電左十幾年 輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bfb4a803d5604bc23aa803ee67bebd9de4e7cd","tid":198930,"uid":15558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"一生充滿電鰻"},{"pid":"412f01457abae60bf6cd9ebaffa18c155e22022e","tid":198930,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:13:15.000Z","msg":"他他佢穩陣wor"},{"pid":"19457ff7017ae45a7a8a7434441b337c2871c383","tid":198930,"uid":48654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一生充滿電鰻</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abea976d92b87b4eae0ccd11a98ec345487682c8","tid":198930,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"唔想check嘅搵厚身膠紙包撚住先啦"}]}